    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="section">
                <head>Original Text</head>
                <figure>
                    <graphic url="../../../Encoding/documents/Images//Birth_Certificate_Small.jpg"
                        width="790px" height="1000px"/>
                </figure>
                <div type="subsection">
                    <pb n="1" facs="#Birth_Certificate.jpg"/>
                    <head place="above">Official Extract</head>
                    <p> Released from <hi rend="italic underline" facs="#matareyaBureau">Al-Matareya
                            Health Bureau</hi>
                        <lb/>Name and place of residence of the applicant <hi
                            rend="italic underline">Sheikh Mohammed Al-Sayyid Al-Najdi</hi>
                        <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/>
                        <hi rend="italic underline">Al-Matareya</hi>
                        <lb/>The subject of which the extract is required <hi
                            rend="italic underline">Birth certificate of his son Ali</hi>
                        <lb/>Extracted from the book of <hi rend="italic underline">birth records of
                            Al-Matareya Health Bureau</hi>
                        <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/> In the year <hi rend="italic underline"
                            >1926</hi>
                        <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/> Page <hi rend="italic underline">75</hi>
                        <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/> Part <hi rend="italic underline"
                            >first</hi>
                        <lb/>Date of permission to give the extract__________ <space quantity="9"
                            unit="chars"/> In the year 192_ <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/>
                        Number__________ <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/> Of__________ <space
                            quantity="9" unit="chars"/>
                        <lb/>Collected fees <hi rend="italic underline">0120 Millime</hi> Warrant
                        number <hi rend="italic underline">114794</hi> On <hi
                            rend="italic underline">11th of April</hi> In the year <hi
                            rend="italic underline">1926</hi> Treasury of <hi
                            rend="italic underline">Al-Matareya Health Bureau</hi>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div type="subsection">
                    <head place="above">The Requested Extract</head>
                    <p> Upon searching, it was found that the aforementioned records affirmatively
                        confirmed the presence on the date of the eighth of April of the year
                        one-thousand nine-hundred (900) <lb/>and twenty six (6) AD under the number
                        274 the name Ali with the name of the father being Mohammed Al-Sayyid
                        Al-Najdi <lb/>of a Muslim religion, Egyptian nationality, scientist as an
                        occupation and the name of the mother being Zainab Soliman <lb/>Al-Rayyes of
                        a Muslim religion, Egyptian nationality, none as an occupation dated
                        <lb/>the eighth of November in the year one-thousand nine-hundred (900)
                        AD... <lb/>The newborn was undocumented on birth, and executing upon a court
                        ruling of the courthouse in Esna to which the Esna Prosecution office 5051
                        <lb/>is affiliated, first number April of the year 1926 on 483 </p>
                </div>
                <div type="subsection">
                    <head place="above">Footer</head>
                    <p> True copy <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/>Released on <hi
                            rend="italic underline">4/11</hi>In the year 192<hi
                            rend="italic underline">6</hi><space quantity="9" unit="chars"
                        />(Signature of the writer) <lb/>Handed over without the governmentâ€™s
                        responsibility whatsoever on what is included within and the rights of
                        others <lb/>(Signature of the pen heads)<space quantity="9" unit="chars"
                        />(Signature of the head of the department or the manager or the governor)
                        <lb/>Released on <hi rend="italic underline">the 17th of April</hi> in the
                        year 192<hi rend="italic underline">6</hi>
                        <lb/>Stamp of the body from which the extract was issued <lb/>(Amiri Press
                        6230/1920/15000) </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="section">
                <head>Description and Breakdown</head>
                <div type="subsection">
                    <head place="above">Who</head>
                    <p>This section describes the people mentioned within the document</p>
                    <list type="bulleted">
                        <item>Ali Mohammed El-Najdy</item>
                        <item>Sheikh Mohammed Al-Sayyid El-Najdi</item>
                        <item>Zainab Soliman Al-Rayyes</item>
                    </list>
                    <table>
                        <row>
                            <cell role="label">Name</cell>
                            <cell role="label">Relation</cell>
                            <cell role="label">Date of Birth</cell>
                            <cell role="label">Occupation</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell role="data">Ali Mohammed Al-Najdi</cell>
                            <cell role="data">Son</cell>
                            <cell role="data">1900</cell>
                            <cell role="data">Teacher/Schoolmaster</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell facs="#mohammedElnagdy">Mohammed Al-Sayyid Al-Najdi</cell>
                            <cell role="data">Father</cell>
                            <cell role="data">Unknown</cell>
                            <cell role="data">Scientist (Islamic Theologian)</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell role="data">Zainab Soliman Al-Rayyes</cell>
                            <cell role="data">Mother</cell>
                            <cell role="data">Unknown</cell>
                            <cell role="data">None</cell>
                        </row>
                    </table>

                    <div type="subsection">
                        <head place="above">The Son</head>
                        <listPerson>
                            <person>
                                <persName>
                                    <forename>Ali</forename>
                                    <surname>Al-Najdi</surname>
                                    <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/>
                                </persName>
                                <birth when="1900-11-08">8th of November 1900</birth>
                                <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/>
                                <sex value="male">Male</sex>
                            </person>
                        </listPerson>
                    </div>
                    <div type="subsection">
                        <head place="above">The Father</head>
                        <listPerson>
                            <person>
                                <persName>
                                    <forename>Sheikh Mohammed</forename>
                                    <surname>Al-Sayyed Al-Najdi</surname>
                                    <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/>
                                </persName>
                                <birth>Unknown</birth>
                                <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/>
                                <sex value="male">Male</sex>
                            </person>
                        </listPerson>
                    </div>
                    <div type="subsection">
                        <head place="above">The Mother</head>
                        <listPerson>
                            <person>
                                <persName>
                                    <forename>Zeinab</forename>
                                    <surname>Soliman Al-Rayyes</surname>
                                    <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/>
                                </persName>
                                <birth>Unknown</birth>
                                <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/>
                                <sex value="female">Female</sex>
                            </person>
                        </listPerson>
                    </div>
                    <div type="subsection">
                        <head>Notes</head>
                        <list>
                            <item><note>"Sheikh" in this context is not a name, but rather a title
                                    used to refer to an Islamic scholar or a person whose job is to
                                    lead the people in prayer (used interchangebly with Imam).
                                    Sometimes "Sheikh" refers to a person of old age, but is used to
                                    refer to an Islamic scholar in this case.</note></item>

                            <item><note>"Al-Sayyed" in this context is not a name, but rather a
                                    title used to refer to a family name; the word is equivalent to
                                    "sir" in English</note></item>

                            <item><note>The date of birth of the father and mother is unknown
                                    specifically, but it is believed to be around the
                                    1870s-1880s</note></item>
                        </list>
                    </div>

                    <note>The word <hi rend="italic">scientist</hi> in this text refers to a scholar
                        of Islamic theology, and often Sheikh in Al-Azhar mosque</note>
                </div>
                <div type="subsection">
                    <head place="above">When</head>
                    <div>
                        <head type="subsection">Dates Mentioned</head>
                        <table>
                            <row>
                                <cell role="label">Date</cell>
