                                    records</cell>
                            </row>
                        </table>
                    </div>

                </div>
                <div type="subsection">
                    <head place="above">Where</head>

                    <div type="subsection">
                        <head place="above">Name-Place References</head>
                        <p>The word "Al-Najdi" refers to someone who comes from Najd, which is the
                            place that forms the center of what is now Saudi Arabia. Najdis, as
                            people, predate Saudi Arabia as a nation and presence of tribes in the
                            area predate many world civilizations dating back to the Neolithic
                            era.</p>
                        <figure>
                            <graphic
                                url="../../../Encoding/documents/Images/1024px-Najd_Region_in_Saudi_Arabia.svg.png"
                            />
                        </figure>
                        <p>Originally, Najd was home to Al-Magar, an advanced culture dating back to
                            the Neolithic era. Reminants of the civilization date back to <date>9000
                                BC</date></p>
                    </div>

